  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Button
    The Button class represents an interactive button element on the canvas.
    Canvas
    This Canvas class represents a physical canvas upon which a user can draw.
    Flipbook
    The Flipbook class is a representation of a flipbook, which is a sequence of frames.
    Frame
    The frame represents one frame of the animation in the flipbook.
    Line
    This Line class represents a squiggle, or amorphous line.
    Main
    This main class connects all other classes within the project, calling all draw methods and instantiating each object as the canvas is used.
